source("mods/plots.R")

speakers <- debates %>% count(speaker, sort = T)
frontrunners <- speakers$speaker[1:5]

Word Counts

debates %>% 
  filter(speaker %in% frontrunners) %>% 
  count_words() %>%
  plot_word_counts()

Applause

debates %>% 
  filter(speaker %in% frontrunners) %>% 
  count_applauses() %>%
  plot_applause_counts

Laughter

debates %>% 
  filter(speaker %in% frontrunners) %>% 
  count_laughs() %>%
  plot_laugh_counts

Cross Talk

debates %>% 
  filter(speaker %in% frontrunners) %>% 
  count_talks() %>%
  plot_talk_counts
